x=     | (1-v)   v
   ------------------
  (1-u)|   x00  x01
     u |   x10  x11
     
     
 y=    | (1-v)   v
   ------------------
  (1-u)|   y00  y01
     u |   y10  y11   
     
 1=    | (1-v)   v
   ------------------
  (1-u)|   1     1
     u |   1     1 
     
     
 a0*x^2+a1*y^2+a2*z^2+a3*x*y+a4*x*z+a5*y*z+a6*x+a7*y+a8*z=1
 
 x^2  ---> convolution(x,x)
 x    ---> conv(x,1)
 
 
 
